{"tid":439655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李飛：噓國歌違基本法危害國家　追溯與否視乎人大決定","createTime":"2017-10-18T04:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T03:16:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4195fd3a8442f0cee68c8fb77bf201e7fcc2d849","tid":439655,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"本港將要因應內地通過的《國歌法》而訂立相關本地法例，特首林鄭月娥昨指本港法例並非很多有追溯期，但例如印花稅修訂草案就有，被批評以民事條例類比國歌法的刑事法例是「不知所謂」。港澳辦前主任王光亞昨明言噓國歌是嚴重違法，今日他再指「對於任何一個國家的國民來說，尊重國家、國歌和國旗，是基本要求」。至於國歌法是否有追溯期，王光亞認為香港可以根據本身的法治制度來考慮。<br />\n<br />\n同樣在北京的基本法委員會主任李飛表示，噓國歌的行為違反基本法、危害國家，下一次全國人大常委會，即明年3月，將會通過將國歌法列入基本法附件三，到時一切會根據有關決定。民主派已計劃就《國歌法》本地立法在立法會提休會辯論。"},{"pid":"d85f4389340829d8e093e801a67156e60a719100","tid":439655,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57346128&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57346128%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171018&d=u3ii42TOxFjH6%2FPSemRc4%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=4b659d51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57346128%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171018&h=951c2913\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57346128&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171018</a>"},{"pid":"afb802f2e40f770a205797b58af44de846c44739","tid":439655,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669643b6f8f2470f31bb86beffd0961e6dd8a0a4","tid":439655,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"喜迎帝制重現"},{"pid":"8cc254289add9d1e392b2b564be416976f04ba2b","tid":